WEBVTT

00:10.240 --> 00:12.307
<i>Previously on The Pillars of the Earth...</i>

00:15.712 --> 00:17.646
Who will rule once I am gone?

00:17.647 --> 00:19.915
There's the king's legitimate daughter, Maud,

00:19.916 --> 00:21.116
then there's me.

00:21.117 --> 00:23.018
The shipwreck was convenient.

00:23.019 --> 00:25.888
What happened was ordained
by God. No one survived.

00:26.956 --> 00:28.624
- My Lord!
- The king is unwell!

00:28.625 --> 00:30.859
- The king is dead.
- Long live the king.

00:30.860 --> 00:33.996
We'll raise an army together
and take Stephen by surprise.

00:35.465 --> 00:37.900
So if you make me Prior,

00:37.901 --> 00:39.701
I make you Bishop?

00:39.702 --> 00:41.670
- My name is Ellen.
- Tom.

00:41.671 --> 00:43.071
Tom the Builder.

00:43.072 --> 00:44.439
She's a witch!

00:44.440 --> 00:46.708
There's work at the Bishop's palace.

00:46.709 --> 00:48.644
- It does need repair.
- Hire this man.

00:48.645 --> 00:49.912
Who is that?

00:49.913 --> 00:51.847
The way to my daughter's heart

00:51.848 --> 00:53.115
<i>is through affection.</i>

00:53.116 --> 00:55.150
We will loot Shiring Castle.

00:55.151 --> 00:56.552
We must defend the king!

00:56.553 --> 00:57.753
You're under attack!

01:01.057 --> 01:03.692
Thank you, Earl of Shiring.

